    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "Skill",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Normal Attack</span><br>Mengakibatkan 2 poin <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/19/25750596/94aa30ae75b8c7c6a9c64ab05bd5dda7_7828749023108688177.png",
                "id": "talent39498",
                "key": "Rapid Ritesword",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Rapid Ritesword"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 3 poin<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\"> Anemo DMG</span>. Penggunaan pertama kali pada setiap Ronde akan memulihkan 2 poin HP kepada diri sendiri jika Karakter memiliki 8 poin HP atau lebih sedikit, tetapi juga akan memberikan status <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Overawing Assault</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Overawing Assault</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Status</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Tahap Selesai:</span> Jika Karakter memiliki 6 poin HP atau lebih, akan menerima 2 poin <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Piercing DMG</span>. </p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Durasi (Ronde): 1</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/19/25750596/42bfd225eedc984bb1d4a4af99e3dcae_3658089198183311966.png",
                "id": "talent53530",
                "key": "Enigmatic Feint",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Enigmatic Feint"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 2 poin <span style=\"color: #80FFD7\">Anemo DMG</span> dan memanggil <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Bogglecat Box</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/19/25750596/b718fd9ceee2d78fdf5d76f345458f71_5394473170321903142.png",
                "id": "talent92572",
                "key": "Magic Trick: Astonishing Shift",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Magic Trick: Astonishing Shift"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Panggilan</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Tahap Selesai:</span> Mengakibatkan 1 poin <span style=\"color: #80FFD7\">Anemo DMG</span>.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan: 2</span></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Saat Karakter aktifmu menerima DMG:</span> Mengurangi 1 poin DMG. (Sekali setiap Ronde)</p><p>Saat Karakter-mu menerima <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span>/<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>/<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>/<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">DMG:</span> Ubah jenis elemen kartu ini menjadi jenis elemen diterima. (Sekali sebelum meninggalkan arena)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/19/25750596/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_5521518114682246401.png",
                "id": "talent77972",
                "key": "Bogglecat Box",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/19/25750596/bc84abe7e3d8d79c9b75a0de329313dc_4729258877283773773.png",
                "title": "Bogglecat Box"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Bereaksi dengan Elemen jika sudah diberikan:</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Cryo Swirl</span>: Mengakibatkan 1 poin Cryo DMG kepada seluruh Karakter lawan selain daripada target</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Hydro Swirl</span>: Mengakibatkan 1 poin Hydro DMG kepada seluruh Karakter lawan selain daripada target<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Pyro Swirl</span>: Mengakibatkan 1 poin Pyro DMG kepada seluruh Karakter lawan selain daripada target<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Electro Swirl</span>: Mengakibatkan 1 poin Electro DMG kepada seluruh Karakter lawan selain daripada target</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/19/25750596/c97292d96456bfe4abeca16bfce801e4_3310447687287577704.png",
                "id": "talent11023",
                "key": "Anemo DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Anemo DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Physical DMG</span></strong></p><p>Physical DMG tidak dapat memberikan elemen apa pun dan memicu Reaksi Elemental.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Piercing DMG</span></strong></p><p>Piercing DMG tidak dapat dipengaruhi oleh Bonus DMG apa pun, namun tidak dapat ditahan oleh efek seperti Perisai atau kekebalan DMG.</p><p><br><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Durasi (Ronde)</span></strong></p><p>Setiap kali kamu mencapai Tahap Selesai di setiap Ronde, <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Durasi (Ronde)</span> -1.</p><p>Kartu ini akan langsung dibuang setelah <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Durasi (Ronde)</span> habis.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Penggunaan</span></strong></p><p>Setelah efek kartu ini dipicu, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan</span>-nya akan dikonsumsi.</p><p>Kartu ini akan langsung dibuang setelah semua <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan</span> telah dikonsumsi.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/19/25750596/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_9217092137224490500.png",
                "id": "talent42515",
                "key": "Detail Peraturan",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Detail Peraturan"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
